install yaourt ::


sudo pacman -S fakeroot
git clone https://aur.archlinux.org/package-query.git
cd package-query
makepkg -si
git clone https://aur.archlinux.org/yaourt.git
cd yaourt
makepkg -si

install pacaur::
git clone https://aur.archlinux.org/pacaur.git
makepkg -si

if you get libalpm11.0 not found 
pacman -R package-query yaour 
then reinstall theme again
